imdb.plot outline: A modest and humble curator at the Smithsonian Institute, Paul Taylor (Dean Dawson) is made aware of the value and historical significance of Royal Seals that have been recovered after having been stolen by an American soldier, 50 years earlier, during the Korean War. Mystery and intrigue follows the path of these priceless artifacts return to their rightful location in Korea.
imdb.title: Royal Seals
